{
  "stem": "12868.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They shoot them, put gasoline, and they burned her up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this is the way they told me how my parents were between [? them ?] where they did it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This is the reason I know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Estonia, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Estonia, they killed all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the one thing-- my-- my youngest brother, he was a singer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was 13 years old.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He got to be bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's when the Germans came with-- the same-- the same day that the bar mitzvah-- when the Germans come in to Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He didn't have the bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he was a singer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He used to sing solo by himself in-- in the biggest congregation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only he sang even in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, the Germans didn't kill him for nine months in Estonia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They killed my parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Only he hid him-- the commandant from the ghetto-- he hid him for three months in-- in his inner room, like an animal, only to sing for him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And later they found out-- the SS found out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They killed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the-- and-- and the-- the SS man, they arrested, you know, for loving the Jewish, for wanting to hide him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he got so emotional.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He sang for him, you know, ghetto songs and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They say-- he sang for everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In ghetto, I remember he sang something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody gave him a piece of bread for this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody kissed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or gave him-- what can you give him?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A piece of bread only.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there in Estonia, they kill my parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he kept him for three months, the SS man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He keeped him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- the-- later, the SS found out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
